{"tid":2240300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民向狗屋發射煙花賀禮","createTime":"2020-10-12T14:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T04:49:28.000Z","uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac982bc792e80c8dfd7276da492591591e6b6fe4","tid":2240300,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lUcEfa3SOs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-lUcEfa3SOs&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=d2891e22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lUcEfa3SOs</a><br />\n<br />\n法國首都巴黎近郊一間警署被大約40人襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n事發在距離巴黎市中心東南面約15公里的一間警署，警方發布的片段顯示，有人在當地周末晚，向警署投擲懷疑煙花，又嘗試強行進入警署，但不成功。警署有窗門碎裂，亦有汽車受損；事件中無警務人員受傷，無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方說約40名身分不明人士，利用鐵通及投擲煙花，暴力襲擊警署，又形容是有組織襲擊及向警方開戰。報道說暫時確定不到襲擊者的動機，事發地區毒品問題嚴重，當局致力打擊毒犯。<br />\n<br />\n地方官員就說之前有一宗意外，當地居民不滿警方處理手法，懷疑襲擊與事件有關。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab78aff37dd7f2a35a6971e7a367463e274bbd2","tid":2240300,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eef2db1a878516707279feaafcc330a584d4f7","tid":2240300,"uid":76804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeGRbxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeGRbxG.png&h=4230a239&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbf342d27f1f29e44f6339e95e34e3f965acbf52","tid":2240300,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22eef2db1a878516707279feaafcc330a584d4f7","tid":2240300,"uid":76804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeGRbxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeGR